# BuildBundle.Attributes

**Object**

The attributes that describe a Build Bundles resource.

## Declaration

```swift
object BuildBundle.Attributes
```

## Objects

- **BuildBundle.Attributes.Entitlements**: Entitlement information for your app or App Clip.

## Objects

- **BuildBundle.Relationships**: The relationships of the Build Bundles resource you included in the request and those on which you can operate.
